Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:58.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}世界就像全景畫一樣 展開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:04.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 無論天空有多寬闊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:10.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}如果只有我一人 肯定不會在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:15.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 笑聲迴響在耳邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:23.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}心中充滿溫柔、愉悅的感覺 還有新的預感
